  "title": "Sales Executive (Commercial Sales/Diesel)",
  "description": "<p>This role involves B2B (business-to-business) sales, focused on acquiring new commercial clients and managing existing accounts. Responsibilities include ensuring a consistent and reliable fuel supply to sectors such as transportation, construction, marine, and industrial operations. The role emphasizes achieving sales targets, offering competitive pricing solutions, and building strong, long-term client relationships.</p><p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li><p>Prospecting and cold-calling to find new clients, while nurturing existing accounts to ensure high retention.</p></li><li><p>Build and maintain strong relationships with customers</p></li><li><p>Prepare quotations and follow up on negotiations</p></li><li><p>Achieve assigned sales targets</p></li><li><p>Manage payment follow-ups and collections to ensure healthy cash flow</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>2 years’ sales experience</strong> in Lubricants / Diesel or Related Trade</p></li><li><p>Good communication and negotiation skills</p></li><li><p>Self-motivated, target-driven, and results-oriented</p></li><li><p><strong>Valid Class 3 driving licence required</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Salary & Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic Salary + High Commission (Uncapped) + Transport Allowance</p></li><li><p>Attractive earnings potential for strong performers<br /></p><p>PR & SINGAPOREAN ONLY</p></li></ul>",
